title: Introducing the Nutri Ninja® Nutri Bowl™ DUO™
description: The Nutri Ninja Nutri Bowl DUO makes creating nutritious meals fast, fresh, and easy with the touch of a button.

asset.author: Nutri Ninja
asset.description:
The Nutri Ninja® Nutri Bowl™ DUO™ makes creating nutritious meals fast, fresh, and easy with the touch of a button. 

For more information about the Nutri Ninja® Nutri Bowl™ DUO™, visit ninjakitchen.com

transcripts: Introducing the Nutri ninja duo. Use the cup for nutrient extraction, breakdown whole ingredients for delicious super juices and smoothies and now snap on the bowl so you can pull ingredients together to create your own nutrient fusions with the touch of a button make nutritious dishes fast, fresh, and easy get nutrient extraction and fusion with the Nutri ninja duo.
